# CRUD Page Workflow

## Basic Requirements
- Standardize CRUD pages: filter/search, table/list, detail drawer/modal, create/edit form
- Separate data layer (service) from presentation; schema-drive forms and tables

## Mandatory Actions
- Define columns: visible/hidden, pinned, alignment (text left, numbers right, enums center)
- Pagination: 10/20/50/100 options; preserve state in URL
- Forms: client-side validation + server-side error surfacing; optimistic updates only when safe
- Internationalization: extract labels and messages; avoid inline literals

## Forbidden Behaviors
- Overloaded action columns; more than two primary actions visible without collapse
- Fetching in components without cancellation; missing empty/loading/error states

